{"data":[{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:03:17.000Z","entities":{"mentions":[{"start":64,"end":73,"username":"kana__ah","id":"1892216888148791296"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037651698924269754"],"id":"2037651698924269754","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0},"author_id":"735283061873508353","text":"Claude Codeにキーワード突っ込むだけで記事からX投稿まで下書き吐き出してくれるツール作ったってことだよな\n\n(via @kana__ah)"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:03:16.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037651695010807908"],"id":"2037651695010807908","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0},"author_id":"2032992293423321088","entities":{"urls":[{"start":174,"end":197,"url":"https://t.co/yq7W0pml2C","expanded_url":"https://twitter.com/_weidai/status/2037387388968960183","display_url":"x.com/_weidai/status…"}]},"text":"I use both daily. The real split: Claude Code for greenfield architecture, Codex for grunt work in existing repos. Neither is winning — they serve different cognitive loads. https://t.co/yq7W0pml2C"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:03:03.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037651639205544197"],"id":"2037651639205544197","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":5},"author_id":"155369088","text":"Claude Code（AnthropicのAIコーディングツール）を導入したのに、\nチームの生産性が上がっていない。\n\nこの状況に心当たりがあるなら、\n原因はツールではなく「環境設計」にある。\n\nAgentic Engineering（AIエージェントを前提にした開発手法）時代の\nベストプラクティスを11項目フル実装した\nClaude"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:03:00.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037651627050672622"],"id":"2037651627050672622","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":3},"author_id":"1694182941486919680","entities":{"urls":[{"start":131,"end":154,"url":"https://t.co/vBM7rn6JFb","expanded_url":"https://x.com/hiroki_e_0711/status/2037651627050672622/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/vBM7rn6JFb","media_key":"3_2037598461294780416"}]},"text":"今まで基本AIはChatGPTだけ使って月1000万円まで稼ぐことができたんだけど、さらにパワーアップしていくために遂にClaude Codeをお迎えした。僕の手法にClaude Code加わったら最強なヤツができちゃうんじゃね？\uD83D\uDE0Fゴリゴリやっちゃうよーんww https://t.co/vBM7rn6JFb"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:02:25.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037651479918530891"],"id":"2037651479918530891","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":1,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":4},"author_id":"1912488042725797891","entities":{"urls":[{"start":158,"end":181,"url":"https://t.co/3wySTWfBYo","expanded_url":"https://x.com/NANDS_AI/status/2037651479918530891/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/3wySTWfBYo","media_key":"3_2037651421634740224"}]},"text":"Claude Code v2.1.86、地味だけど「運用側が救われる」アップデートだと思う\uD83D\uDCA1  \nAPIリクエストに `X-Claude-Code-Session-Id` が付くようになって、プロキシやゲートウェイでボディ覗かずにセッション単位の集計ができる。これ、監査・課金・障害解析の設計が一段ラクになるやつ。 https://t.co/3wySTWfBYo"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:02:07.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037651404580343879"],"id":"2037651404580343879","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":1,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":4},"author_id":"2026735888794005508","text":"Everyone's debating Cursor vs Claude Code.\n\nMeanwhile, Faros AI tracked 10,000+ developers and found: AI adoption = 91% longer PR review times, 154% larger PRs, 9% more bugs, zero measurable impact on org velocity.\n\nThe tool war is real. It's just happening at the wrong level of"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:02:00.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037651375362904467"],"id":"2037651375362904467","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":1},"author_id":"1070650761732796417","text":"Claude Codeのスキル、今日また新しいの入れてみたんだけど、気づいたら「作業する時間」より「何を任せるか考える時間」のほうが長くなってた。\nこれって退化してるのか進化してるのかわからなくなってきた。\n\nでも多分、こっちが本来の使い方なんだよな。"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:02:00.000