Codeなどデプロイ自動化ツール「Agent Plugins for AWS」を公開 (ビジネス＋IT)","description":"米Amazon Web ServicesはAIエージェントのClaude CodeやCursorにクラウド環境の設計からデプロイまでの機能を組み込む拡張ツールAgent Plugins for AWSを公開した。開発者がチャットで指示を出すだけでソースコードの解析やインフラ構成の推奨およびコスト見積もりから実際の...","unwound_url":"https://www.smartnews.com/ja-jp/article/4928238734572267782?placement=article-preview-social&utm_campaign=sn_lid%3A4928238734572267782%7Csn_channel%3Acr_ja_top&utm_source=share_ios_twitter&share_id=bs89gZ"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037651313249644616"],"id":"2037651313249644616","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":5},"author_id":"126853543","text":"\"米AWSがClaude Codeなどデプロイ自動化ツール「Agent Plugins for AWS」を公開\" - ビジネス＋IT #SmartNews  https://t.co/yh3ZQjZLmV"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:01:30.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037651251794759687"],"id":"2037651251794759687","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":9},"author_id":"4720427994","entities":{"urls":[{"start":68,"end":91,"url":"https://t.co/JvQSE3vwGt","expanded_url":"https://twitter.com/lydiahallie/status/2037573738670297583","display_url":"x.com/lydiahallie/st…"}]},"text":"最近 Claude Codeのhooks関連を色々触りたいなぁって思っていて、そんな中ifフィールドがサポートされた。これは面白そう。 https://t.co/JvQSE3vwGt"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:01:19.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037651205481206058"],"id":"2037651205481206058","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":1,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":8},"author_id":"1261574216157032449","text":"\"There is no compression algorithm for human experience still.\"\n\nClaude Code is quietly turning a lot of us into better staff and senior engineers. \n\nYou stop grinding out boilerplate and start spending your time on architecture, tradeoffs, and high level design. The AI handles"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:01:00.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037651123