i-ne…","status":200,"title":"Weekly AI News #2026-03-27","description":"生成系の動向と組織運用の変革を総括する報告書的展望と実務示唆","unwound_url":"https://ainewsdev.substack.com/p/weekly-ai-news-2026-03-27"},{"start":181,"end":204,"url":"https://t.co/Eh1clgv884","expanded_url":"https://techcrunch.com/2026/03/26/wikipedia-cracks-down-on-the-use-of-ai-in-article-writing/","display_url":"techcrunch.com/2026/03/26/wik…","images":[{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2037286373804453888/hztPX4FD?format=jpg&name=orig","width":1200,"height":800},{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2037286373804453888/hztPX4FD?format=jpg&name=150x150","width":150,"height":150}],"status":200,"title":"Wikipedia cracks down on the use of AI in article writing | TechCrunch","description":"The site, whose policies are subject to change, has struggled with the issue of AI-generated writing.","unwound_url":"https://techcrunch.com/2026/03/26/wikipedia-cracks-down-on-the-use-of-ai-in-article-writing/"}]},"text":"\uD83D\uDCF0 自分で読む為のAIニュース [1-10/35]\n========================================\n\n1. 週刊AIニュース #2026-03-27 - hotchpotch著\n\uD83D\uDCCE https://t.co/bE69CVzmWL\n\n2. Wikipediaが記事作成におけるAIの使用を取り締まる | TechCrunch\n\uD83D\uDCCE https://t.co/Eh1clgv884\n\n3. Claude CodeとDevinをFour"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:00:12.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037650921476510187"],"id":"2037650921476510187","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":3},"author_id":"2003275986037846016","text":"2026年3月時点のAI開発ツール選び方。\n\nターミナル派 → Claude Code\nIDE統合派 → Cursor\nGitHub中心 → Copilot\n全自動がいい → Devin\n無料で試したい → Windsurf（SWE-1.5が3ヶ月無料）\n\n正解は「1つに絞る」ことじゃない。\n用途で使い分けるのが最強。\n\n僕はClaude Code + Cursorの二刀流。"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:00:02.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037650880342933990"],"id":"2037650880342933990","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":5},"author_id":"1694821393068924930","entities":{"urls":[{"start":151,"end":174,"url":"https://t.co/WTDUtYwa8R","expanded_url":"https://x.com/shinmomo0512/status/2037650880342933990/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/WTDUtYwa8R","media_key":"3_2037620042037383168"}]},"text":"Claudeにやらせてみた\uD83D\uDC40\nブクマ推奨\n\nClaude Codeに「動画作って」と言ったら、\n本当に動画が出てきた。\n\nRemotion Skillsという仕組みで、\nReactベースのコードをClaude Codeが自動生成、\nそのまま動画としてレンダリングされる。\n\nコードは1行も書いてない。 https://t.co/WTDUtYwa8R"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:00:01.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037650878895968456"],"id":"2037650878895968456","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":2,"impression_count":43},"author_id":"1405031034","entities":{"urls":[{"start":281,"end":304,"url":"https://t.co/ousSdMdbQe","expanded_url":"https://x.com/JulianGoldieSEO/status/2037650878895968456/video/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/ousSdMdbQe","media_key":"13_2037480447480053761"}]},"text":"Claude Code just changed the game.\n\nAI stopped asking for permission on every tiny step.\n\nThe new Auto Mode decides what is safe, executes it, and only stops when something is actually risky.\n\nThat means no more:\n\n“Can I edit this file?”\n\n“Can I run this command?”\n\n“Can I install https://t.co/ousSdMdbQe"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:00:01.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037650876551061805"],"id":"2037650876551061805","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":6},"author_id":"1479852652150337542","entities":{"urls":[{"start":184,"end":207,"url":"https://t.co/50lYEb2MuD","expanded_url":"https://x.com/Michaelzsguo/status/2037650876551061805/video/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/50lYEb2MuD","media_key":"13_2037565802615029760"}]},"text":"我大胆预测一下： Claude Code 团队两天内就会把这功能学过去。\n\nCoding Agent Cline刚刚发布了开源的Cline Kanban，直接把 coding agent 的用法往前推了一大步。\n\n当下用Coding Agent的痛点其实很明显。譬如你用 Claude Code 写代码，很多时候不是在写，而是在等。一个 agent 跑 8 到 10 https://t.co/50lYEb2MuD"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:00:01.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037650875632722077"],"id":"2037650875632722077","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":3},"author_id":"1158064998255480832","entities":{"urls":[{"start":142,"end":165,"url":"https://t.co/TcsOYxADwQ","expanded_url":"https://twitter.com/oikon48/status/2037486034087485636","display_url":"x.com/oikon48/status…"}]},"text":"これ知らずにAGENTS.mdを書いてた人、今すぐ確認しろ。Claude Codeが自動で読むのはCLAUDE.mdだけだ。AGENTS.mdを参照させたいなら@`Importで明示的に取り込む必要がある。ルールを書いても届いていない状態で仕事させてたかもしれない。今日から変わる。 https://t.co/TcsOYxADwQ"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:00:00.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037650872466076028"],"id":"2037650872466076028","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0},"author_id":"2015836209730535424","text":"Claude Code、ターミナルで\"claude\"って打つだけでAIペアプログラマーが起動する。\n\nCursorみたいにエディタ切り替え不要。既存のワークフローに乗せられるのが強い。\n\nCLAUDE.mdにプロジェクトルール書いておけば、毎回「TypeScriptで書いて」とか言わなくていい。設定ファイル1つで精度が激変する。"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:59:16.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037650688516252082"],"id":"2037650688516252082","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":1},"author_id":"1721619111195910144","text":"Shipped a promo code system for the DAM nutrition app in one day. Our team can now give free Premium access to affiliates with a code. It took about one day of work with Claude code and the iOS mcp for app testing."},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:59:15.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037650685765042615"],"id":"2037650685765042615","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":3},"author_id":"1620098280851120128","entities":{"urls":[{"start":0,"end":23,"url":"https://t.co/kX0KD4dmQ4","expanded_url":"https://github.com/caseyrtalbot/forge","d