ude Code Dega"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:56:41.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037650038692917432"],"id":"2037650038692917432","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":16},"author_id":"1176768396668465152","text":"Claude Codeを使っている人は全員これを読んだ方がいい！\n\nみたいな記事正直今は1ミリも理解できないから興味ないけど、これ全部Obsidianに clippingしておけば、将来の自分が助かるのかもしれないし、不要でもかかる労力はワンポチだけだしーー"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:56:22.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037649956669170096"],"id":"2037649956669170096","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":7},"author_id":"1872272587738529792","entities":{"urls":[{"start":98,"end":121,"url":"https://t.co/EbK8ersa7I","expanded_url":"https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=47545642","display_url":"news.ycombinator.com/item?id=475456…","status":200,"title":"Show HN: Open-Source Animal Crossing–Style UI for Claude Code Agents | Hacker News","description":"We posted here on Monday and got some great feedback. We’ve implemented a few of the most requested updates: - iMessage channel support (agents can text people and you c an text agents) Other channels are simple to extend. - A built-in browser (agents can navigate and interact with websites) - Scheduling (run tasks on a timer / cron / in the future) - Built in tunneling so that the agents can share local stuff with you over the internet - More robust MCP and Skills support so anyone can extend it - Auto","unwound_url":"https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=47545642"}]},"text":"Claude Codeエージェント用のオープンソースUI。Animal Crossing風UX、iMessage連携、組み込みブラウザ、スケジューリング、トンネル機能、拡張、リクエスト自動承認。 https://t.co/EbK8ersa7I"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:55:58.000Z","entities":{"mentions":[{"start":68,"end":72,"username":"kit","id":"1139753100"}],"urls":[{"start":75,"end":98,"url":"https://t.co/lMcroGpvFi","expanded_url":"https://x.com/CasJam/status/2037649856240525744/video/1","display_url":"p