he previous Code with Claude event on May 22, 2025, Anthropic held an opening keynote where they announced the Claude 4 series of models\n\nI wonder if we will get some news or potential reveals about the Claude Mythos https://t.co/ctWRN5s3P6 https://t.co/ZXE2sTQOnD"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:55:38.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037649775542341999"],"id":"2037649775542341999","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":24},"author_id":"935828365122195457","entities":{"urls":[{"start":279,"end":302,"url":"https://t.co/phRLIECxiW","expanded_url":"https://x.com/KimNoel399/status/2037649775542341999/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/phRLIECxiW","media_key":"3_2037649771872268288"},{"start":279,"end":302,"url":"https://t.co/phRLIECxiW","expanded_url":"https://x.com/KimNoel399/status/2037649775542341999/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/phRLIECxiW","media_key":"3_2037649772149170176"},{"start":279,"end":302,"url":"https://t.co/phRLIECxiW","expanded_url":"https://x.com/KimNoel399/status/2037649775542341999/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/phRLIECxiW","media_key":"3_2037649771989471232"},{"start":279,"end":302,"url":"https://t.co/phRLIECxiW","expanded_url":"https://x.com/KimNoel399/status/2037649775542341999/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/phRLIECxiW","media_key":"3_2037649772622831616"}]},"text":"J'ai cramé 120€ dans l'API Claude fast et je peux vous dire que ça vaut pas le coup. \n24 M de tokens consommés en 2h à peine. \nCe n'est pas aussi rapide que sur Cerebras et c'est extrêmement cher. Le mode fast n'est utilisable dans Claude Code que si on paie avec l'API, non pas https://t.co/phRLIECxiW"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:54:51.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037649575687999549"],"id":"2037649575687999549","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":1,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":2,"impression_count":170},"author_id":"1292995835966312448","entities":{"urls":[{"start":139,"end":162,"url":"https://t.co/n5gVWK45B1","expanded_url":"https://twitter.com/kawai_design/status/2037520290474025416","display_url":"x.com/kawai_design/s…"}]},"text":"【 Claude Code の設計手法 】\n\n私は毎週、PCのフォルダやClaude Code関連のファイル構造をClaude Codeに改善してもらっています。\n\n昨日は、ハーネス設計を導入。実際にどう変わったか？詳しく記事に書きました。設定ファイルの一部も公開しています。 https://t.co/n5gVWK45B1"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:54:50.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037649574245052601"],"id":"2037649574245052601","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":2,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":7},"author_id":"1894723460812935168","text":"何度でも言います。\nChatGPTだけで全部こなそうとしてる人、\n2026年はかなり苦しくなると思う。\n\n実際に結果出してる人を見てると、\nちゃんと使い分けてるんよね↓\n\n・ネタ・アイデア出し　→ Gemini\n・文章・記事をつくる　→ Claude\n・ツール作成・自動化　→ Claude Code\n・最新情報のリサーチ　→"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:54:00.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037649361878839397"],"id":"2037649361878839397","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":1,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":83},"author_id":"1292995835966312448","text":"Anthropicが公式で\n「ハーネス設計」の記事を出した。\n\n↓ 核心はこれ\n\n「AIは自分の成果物を評価すると甘くなる。\nだから作る役と評価する役を分けろ」\n\nこれを自分のClaude Codeに\n実装してみました。\n\n↓やったこと\n\n・HTMLを書いた瞬間にPlaywrightで\n　自動スクショ→検証するHook"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:54:00.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037649361669066989"],"id":"2037649361669066989","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":5},"author_id":"1789633726974201856","text":"Claude codeとgeminiで\n\nKindle出版、初めてやってみた。\n\n画像生成→台本→製本→アップロード。一通りの流れを把握するのに丸2日かかった。\n\nでも2冊目からは企画リサーチに時間を割ける。\n\n「1回目は遅くていい。全体を知ることが目的」って自分に言い聞かせてる。"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:53:59.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037649357013500000"],"id":"2037649357013500000","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":1,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":14},"author_id":"1348438177","text":"This week’s recap bulletin\n\n\uD83E\uDD16Claude - moving to Claude, built a new test project with Claude Code, created a custom skill\n\uD83E\uDD9ETikTok x OpenClaw - 10k views total, still improving flow, slowly growing\n\uD83C\uDFACPersonal TikTok - idea to make slide content, not ready for filming yet"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:53:26.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037649220870488393"],"id":"2037649220870488393","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":6,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":5,"impression_count":91},"author_id":"1115454750399578112","entities":{"urls":[{"start":279,"end":302,"url":"https://t.co/3pS3Bsoei4","expanded_url":"https://x.com/altmemy199/status/2037649220870488393/video/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/3pS3Bsoei4","media_key":"7_2037649138318196736"}]},"text":"تخيلوا صار الآن تقدر تستنسخ أي موقع تقريبًا \n\nمطور سوّى skill لـ Claude Code يخليه يشوف الموقع عبر Chrome MCP وبعدين يبني له نسخة منه. دالـ AI يسحب الخطوط، والألوان، والليآوت، ويقسم الموقع إلى أجزاء، ويكررها، وبعدها يركب كل شيء فوق بعض ويطلع لك النتيجة جاهزة.\n\nما يسرق بس يستلهم https://t.co/3pS3Bsoei4"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:53:09.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037649147331789259"],"id":"2037649147331789259","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":30},"author_id":"27689872","entities":{"urls":[{"start":276,"end":299,"url":"https://t.co/nSq77O8YsS","expanded_url":"https://x.com/_TheJasonC/status/2037649147331789259/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/nSq77O8YsS","media_key":"3_2037649144966426624"}]},"text":"A new feature in Claude Cowork and Claude Code will allow the AI to quite literally use your computer to perform tasks on your behalf. \n\nThis includes opening files, using the browser, running tools, etc. \n\nClaude can use your keyboard and mouse to scroll, perform input, and https://t.co/nSq77O8YsS"},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:53:00.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037649112917